## Context
Wave-1 move of the code reorg epic (tracker `0240`). Relocate the `qa_*` **entry
points** into `scripts/qa/`. Only Tier-3 entry points (per the 0254 audit) move;
imported library modules stay flat.

## Depends on 0253 + 0254
- `0253` installs the relative source-root path model (subdir imports resolve).
- `0254` publishes the Tier-2/Tier-3 list — the contract for what moves.

## Semantic-phase note (architecture.md § "Phase is semantic")
The `qa_` prefix sits in the Phase-1 prefix table, but phase is what the script
*does*:
- `qa_embeddings.py`, `qa_detect_type.py` emit **Phase-2** outputs
  (`semantic_clusters.csv`, `qa_type_report.csv` → `DERIVED_TABLES_DIR`). The
  directory move to `scripts/qa/` groups them by concern; it does not change
  their phase or their output home.
- `qa_near_duplicates.py` is imported by `corpus_filter` — its 0254
  classification decides whether it moves or its library part is extracted first.
Group by concern, not by asserting a single phase for the folder.

## Relevant files
- `scripts/qa_*.py` — the Tier-3 subset (per 0254)
- `docs/repo-layout.md` — Tier-2/Tier-3 audit table (0254)
- `.claude/rules/architecture.md` § Phase is semantic
- `Makefile` + relevant `.mk` — `qa_*` target script paths to repoint

## Actions
1. `git mv` each Tier-3 `qa_*` entry point into `scripts/qa/`.
2. Repoint every Make target script path to the new location.
3. Leave Tier-2 library modules flat (e.g. an extracted `qa_near_duplicates`
   library part).

## Test
- `make -n` for one `qa_*` target yields the same prereq graph — only the path
  segment changes.
- Moved entry points import + run under `PYTHONPATH=scripts:libs/openalex-corpus/src`.
- `make check` green.

## Invariants
- Only Tier-3 entry points move; Tier-2 modules stay flat.
- No top-level `src/`; no `python -m`; flat module names unchanged.
- Phase semantics unchanged: `qa_embeddings`/`qa_detect_type` still write their
  Phase-2 outputs to `DERIVED_TABLES_DIR`.
- One logical move per PR (this ticket = the qa move only).

## Exit criteria
- All Tier-3 `qa_*` entry points under `scripts/qa/`.
- Every Make script path repointed; no dangling reference.
- `make check` green.

